display_long_description:
Project Funny Monke is a chill, winter-themed fan game inspired by the classic Gorilla Tag experience — but with a frosty twist. Set in a world where every branch is frosted and every hill is coated in fresh powder, Name Here invites players to leap, climb, and explore like never before, all while bundled in cozy winter vibes.

From the moment you load into the game, you’re dropped into a snowy wonderland packed with custom maps, each designed to capture the magic and playfulness of winter. Whether you're racing across icy caves, bouncing through snow-covered forests, or scaling massive frozen mountains, every map is crafted to keep movement feeling fresh, fun, and full of possibilities.

Project Funny Monke isn’t just about the maps though — it's about how you express yourself too. Unlock a huge variety of cosmetics to personalize your look, from colorful scarves and beanies to frosty goggles and even animated snow particle effects. Every session gives you a chance to show off your style while you’re pulling off slick moves across the snowy landscapes.

The game also features unique game modes that bring even more life to the experience. Team up with friends in a cozy game of "Snowball Tag," test your skills in tricky parkour challenges, or jump into relaxed free play sessions where you can just vibe and explore. Whether you're chasing high-energy rounds or just looking to chill out and mess around, there’s always something new to do.
